Residence vs. Ocurrence Analyses

Functions for calculating and visualizing coverage and dose distribution by place of residence or vaccination.

(R)esidence (Oc)currence Coverage
roc_barplot()
(R)esidence (Oc)currence Bar Plot

(R)esidence (Oc)currence Dose Distribution
roc_heatmap()
(R)esidence (Oc)currence Heatmap
roc_coverage_by()
(R)esidence or (Oc)currence Coverage
